  "title": "Tree & Plant Gardener | Landscape Work at Hospitals",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>5.5 Days Per Week | Sunday OFF</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>8am-5pm (Mon to Fri) | 8am to 12pm (Sat)</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Role: Gardener | Tree &amp; Plant Nurturer &amp; Watering</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic Salary: SGD $1,950 [ Can Nego if experiences ]</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Entitled to Medical Benefits &amp; Bonus</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>This role will work under Landscaping &amp; Plantation Company but outsource to work under various hospitals in Singapore. [ Novena | Jurong East | Sengkang | Yishun / Choa Chu Kang ]</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>5 Locations available, can station permanently in one location [ hospital ]</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Must be <em><strong>Covid vaccination certified</strong></em> due to the work environment at hospitals.</li>\n  <li>Prefer those with <em><strong>basic plantation knowledge and gardener experience.</strong></em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Scopes:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Weeding and mulching landscape beds</li>\n  <li>Trimming small trees, hedges and shrubs</li>\n  <li>Removing unwanted, dead or damaged trees</li>\n  <li>Planting shrubs, flowers and trees</li>\n  <li>Watering gardens, lawns and landscapes</li>\n  <li>Grass cutting</li>\n  <li>Fertilizing plants</li>\n  <li>Monitoring and maintaining plant health</li>\n</ol>\n<p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p>\n<p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p>\n<p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
